CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782915514
OL,3,CBuilder jailed for more than two years
OL,4,Cfor defrauding customers more than
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,FA builder from Derby who took more
OL,8,Fthan #200,000 from homeowners while
OL,9,Fknowing his company could not pay its
OL,10,Fdebts has been jailed.
OL,12,FMichael Haslam, 74, ran M&J Builders
OL,13,FLimited when it was insolvent, taking
OL,14,Fmoney upfront from homeowners and not
OL,15,Fcompleting the work he had promised.
OL,17,FDerby Crown Court heard his victims,
OL,18,Fwho often found his company through
OL,19,Fadverts in magazines, paid thousands
OL,20,Fof pounds for home improvements
OL,21,Fbetween 2020 and 2022.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782915514
OL,3,CBuilder jailed for more than two years
OL,4,Cfor defrauding customers more than
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,FSome were left with dangerous
OL,8,Fstructures, no running water and bills
OL,9,Fthey could not afford to fix.
OL,11,FThe court heard Haslam spent
OL,12,Fcustomers' money on cash withdrawals,
OL,13,FAmazon and eBay purchases as well as
OL,14,Fpayments to his own family.
OL,16,FMark Stevens, chief investigator,
OL,17,FInsolvency Service Criminal
OL,18,FInvestigation Team, said: "I think the
OL,19,Fcourt has clearly seen the impact of
OL,20,Fthe offending.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782915514
OL,3,CBuilder jailed for more than two years
OL,4,Cfor defrauding customers more than
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,F"Michael Haslam has committed a
OL,8,Fserious offence of fraudulent trading.
OL,9,FHe has defrauded his victims of more
OL,10,Fthan two-hundred-thousand pounds and
OL,11,Fhopefully, for those victims, justice
OL,12,Fwill seem to have been served, to some
OL,13,Fextent.
OL,15,F"It's been life changing for the
OL,16,Fvictims without a shadow of a doubt.
OL,17,FThey have suffered mentally,
OL,18,Fphysically and financially and had to
OL,19,Flive in homes that haven't been fit
OL,20,Ffor habitation for many months.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782915514
OL,3,CBuilder jailed for more than two years
OL,4,Cfor defrauding customers more than
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,F"We've seen and heard from the victims
OL,8,Fin court here today how poor his work
OL,9,Fwas.
OL,11,F"In many cases people living in single
OL,12,Frooms with families, unsafe
OL,13,Fproperties, unfinished work and he has
OL,14,Fclearly not been of a mind to go back
OL,15,Fand rectify those problems for those
OL,16,Fvictims.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782915514
OL,3,CBuilder jailed for more than two years
OL,4,Cfor defrauding customers more than
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,F"Back in 2020, it was identified that
OL,8,Fhe was taking out loans, he should
OL,9,Fhave seen and read the situation
OL,10,Fclearly, failed to do so and continued
OL,11,Fin his bad behaviour towards his
OL,12,Fvictims.
OL,14,F"I think (the sentence) sends a very
OL,15,Fstrong message out anybody who wants
OL,16,Fto conduct this kind of behaviour."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
