CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782915514
OL,3,CBuilder jailed for more than two years
OL,4,Cfor defrauding customers more than
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,FHaslam, of Oaklands Avenue,
OL,8,FLittleover, pleaded guilty to one
OL,9,Fcount of fraudulent trading in May
OL,10,Fthis year, following investigations by
OL,11,Fthe Insolvency Service.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for two years and four
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
